Text.val: 16.05.2011 SH SCR16448 Replaced GNRL_CURRENCY by ADMN_CURRENCY
05.09.2002 JJ changed hardcoded SQL to use %FACTOLINKLIB% and GNRL_CURRENCY
Program checks INVO_AACTUALx against the corresponding INVA row

SQL_STMT_U.val: select inva_no, invo_admno, invo_clntno, invo_debh_no, invo_debc_no, invo_debc_debc, invo_invoiceno, invo_currency, invo_aactuali, invo_aactualh, clnt108_acc_curr, invo_aactualc, inva_currency, inva_actafactoring, inva_actaspecial from :1/invo, :1/inva, :1/clnt, :1/admn where inva_no = invo_no and clnt101_admno = invo_admno and clnt102_clntno = invo_clntno and admn_no = invo_admno and (inva_currency = invo_currency and inva_actafactoring + inva_actaspecial <> invo_aactuali or inva_currency = admn_currency and inva_actafactoring + inva_actaspecial <> invo_aactualh or inva_currency = clnt108_acc_curr and inva_actafactoring + inva_actaspecial <> invo_aactualc) order by INVA_NO, INVA_CURRENCY for fetch only optimize for 100 rows;
